==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sherryvallies
<hw>Sher"ry*val`lies</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Sp.
<ets>zaraquelles</ets> wide breeches or overalls.]</ety> <def>Trousers
or overalls of thick cloth or leather, buttoned on the outside of each
leg, and generally worn to protect other trousers when riding on
horseback.</def> <mark>[Local, U.S.]</mark>
<rj><au>Bartlett.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

